      • NO_REALM

        public static final String NO_REALM
        To access the default audit service via AuditEventFactory.accessEvent(String) and AuditEventPublisher.isAuditing(String, String, EventName) you can provide null or an empty string. We deliberately do not provide a convenience method with no realm to force implementers to consider providing the realm.

      • OAUTH2_AUDIT_CONTEXT_PROVIDERS
